sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Researcher as [VLM Researcher]
  participant Dashboard as [Dashboard]
  participant Python as [ego-flow Python Package]
  participant Backend as [Backend]
  participant DB as [DB]

  Researcher->>Dashboard: Python static token 발급 요청
  Dashboard->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/python/tokens
  Note over Dashboard,Backend: Headers<br/>Cookie: egoflow_session={dashboard_session}<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/><br/>Body<br/>name: python_token_name

  Backend->>Backend: requireDashboardSession
  Backend->>DB: api_tokens row 생성 또는 rotate
  Note over Backend,DB: user_id = dashboard user id<br/>name = requested token name<br/>token_hash = hash(raw ef_ token)<br/>revoked_at = null
  Backend-->>Dashboard: 201 Created
  Note over Backend,Dashboard: Response Body<br/>id<br/>name<br/>token: ef_raw_python_static_token<br/>created_at<br/>rotated_previous

  Dashboard-->>Researcher: raw ef_ token 표시
  Researcher->>Python: pip install ego-flow 후 token 설정
  Note over Researcher,Python: 현재 package 설정 입력<br/>EF_TOKEN 또는 token 인자<br/>EF_SERVER_ENDPOINT 또는 server_endpoint 인자

  Python->>Python: EgoFlowClient.from_env()
  Note over Python: EgoFlowConfig.from_env()<br/>EF_TOKEN, EF_SERVER_ENDPOINT를 필수로 읽음<br/>api_base_url = {endpoint}/api/v1

  Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/auth/python/tokens/validate
  Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token

  Backend->>Backend: requirePythonToken
  Note over Backend: Bearer token 추출<br/>ef_ prefix 확인<br/>token hash 계산
  Backend->>DB: active API token 조회
  Note over Backend,DB: api_tokens.token_hash match<br/>revoked_at is null<br/>token owner user is not deactivated

  alt token invalid, revoked, or user deactivated
    Backend-->>Python: 401 Unauthorized
    Python->>Python: EgoFlowAuthenticationError
  else token valid
    DB-->>Backend: token owner user
    Backend->>DB: last_used_at 갱신
    Note over Backend,DB: requirePythonToken 처리 중 token 사용 시각 갱신
    Backend-->>Python: 200 OK
    Note over Backend,Python: Response Body<br/>valid: true<br/>user.id<br/>user.role<br/>user.display_name
    Python->>Python: python_user_id() 호출 시 user.id cache
  end

%% 참고:
%% Python package는 id/password login을 수행하지 않는다.
%% Python package는 Dashboard에서 발급된 ef_ static token을 Authorization: Bearer header로 사용한다.
%% 현재 ego-flow-py package distribution name은 pyproject 기준 "ego-flow"이고 import package는 "ego_flow"이다.
%% Python package는 별도 server port 설정을 받지 않는다. 서버 public HTTP는 80번 port 고정 정책을 따른다.
